OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStaying
OL,6,Fwarm and sunny into next week with
OL,7,Flight winds. Likely to be more cloud
OL,8,Fon Sunday which will allow
OL,9,Ftemperatures to dip. Risk of an
OL,10,Fisolated shower Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
